     Autograd derivative chain:
     ```python
     xi_input = xi_bq_flat.detach().requires_grad_(True)
     # ...
     w_xi  = _grad(w, xi_input)       # ∂w/∂ξ
     w_xi2 = _grad(w_xi, xi_input)    # ∂²w/∂ξ²
     u_xi  = _grad(u, xi_input)       # ∂u/∂ξ
